==English==

===Etymology===
From ''to [[work]]'' + ''[[-er]]''.

===Pronunciation===
* ''[[RP]]:'' {{IPA|/ˈwɜːkə/}}
* ''US:'' {{IPA|/ˈwɝkɚ/}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɜː(r)kə(r)|-ɜː(r)kə(r)]]

===Noun===
'''worker'''  (''plural:'' [[workers]])
#A person who performs [[labor]], especially [[manual]] labor.
#A nonreproductive [[ant]], [[bee]], [[termite]] or [[wasp]].

